para_trans: Regarding the assignment of additional charge of the post of "Nagpur."
Department of Higher and Technical Education
GOVERNMENT ORDER NUMBER: SANKARIK-2024 / Q.No. (23/24) / TANSHI-1
Reference: Letter from the Director, Technical Education No. 1 / Director / 2024/19, dated February 05, 2024

Additional charge of the post of "Joint Director, Technical Education Divisional Office, Nagpur" has been given to Dr. Manoj Daigavane, Principal, Government Technical College, Nagpur under this order.
For administrative reasons, the additional charge of the post of Joint Director, Technical Education Divisional Office, Nagpur is being delegated to the officers mentioned in Column-I as under:
3. The said orders shall come into force with immediate effect.
4. The officers concerned shall immediately assume the additional charge assigned to them and communicate the same to the Government through the Director, Technical Education.
The Government decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
